Hi Tonny,

I just received a message from our shipping team that we only have 276 units available to ship and not ETA on when more will be available.

Are you able to work with your sales team and relay this to the customer to see if they are ok with buying 276 for now. If they are, please send us a revised PO to reflect the 276 qty.

Also, is your logistics team able to book the LTL pickup and provide us with the BOL if we send you pallet qty and dimensions?


Regards,
